abstract: Yale men's basketball team defeats Cornell, 62-51; other men's and women's college basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Justin Sears and Armani Cotton had double-doubles, and Javier Duren was two rebounds shy of joining them as Yale (19-7, 8-1 Ivy) won, 62-51, over visiting Cornell (12-13, 3-4).
